title: The Libertines: There Are No Innocent Bystanders (2011) Collecto
description:
The Libertines: There Are No Innocent Bystanders (2011) Collector's Edition [MP4]
--------------------------
An access-all-areas documentary about The Libertines reunion shows at Reading & Leeds Festivals 2010 
from first time director Roger Sargent; photographer, witness and confidante of the band throughout their short and 
turmoil filled career. Featuring the present day story of the build up, rehearsals, warm-ups and concerts set against the 
painfully honest interviews with each band member recounting the band's history and illustrated by Sargent's unparalleled 
archive of classic Libertines photographs. An intense and intimate portrayal of arguably Britain's most exciting and influential band of the last decade.
--------------------------

Disc Two:
